Package: giftwrapr
Type: Package
Title: Jarvis march algorithm for distinct point in the plane
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-03-20
Author: Kristina Bratkova
Maintainer: Kristina Bratkova <kbratkov0@gmail.com>
Description: The package run Jarvis march algorithm on data given by a single vector, a list or a data frame specifying (x,y) coordinates. `jarvis_march()` returns a dataframe of line segments forming the hull, `in_hull()` returns boolean values of points on the hull and `plot_hull()`plots the points and their convex hull.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10)
Depends: Tidyverse (>= 2.0.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
